{"tid":1027143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔撚關我事]韓國瑜稱香港馬會「主動關心高雄賽馬」　馬會發聲明：從未與高雄市政府討論 (","createTime":"2019-02-18T15:14:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T00:02:39.000Z","uid":51271,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"06e87ba100c393053dcfd905bbf88da214780d8d","tid":1027143,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T15:14:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20190218/s00004/1550502389477/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20190218%2Fs00004%2F1550502389477%2F&d=XUHW2qJizO2pFN7N4VPpEmt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=bcce1f6a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20190218%2Fs00004%2F1550502389477%2F&h=6c3bde69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20190218/s00004/1550502389477/</a><br />\n<br />\n台灣高雄市長韓國瑜銳意推動高雄賽馬業，上月更會見香港賽馬會前董事林雋軒「取經」。韓國瑜近日接受台灣《鏡週刊》訪問時表示，香港馬會「主動關心高雄賽馬」，並已為高雄「打造了一個需求表」，包括土地、空間及設施等需求。香港馬會周一（18日）發聲明，澄清從無與高雄市政府討論該市發展賽馬的計劃。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>香港賽馬會並在聲明表示，從無參與韓國瑜提及的土地、空間及設施需求評估等工作；又指任何馬會前僱員就高雄賽馬發展的參與及工作，和他們提供或可能提供的意見，都不代表馬會。<br />\n</strong><br />\n今次已非香港賽馬會首次發表聲明，澄清高雄市政府及韓國瑜就「香港馬會成員」與高雄官員會面的消息。香港馬會前董事林雋軒等人，上月30日與韓國瑜及高雄市政府人員會面，高雄市政府起初發布的行程顯示，當日下午「香港賽馬會」至市府拜會，高雄觀光局長潘恆旭亦舌傳媒稱「香港賽馬會」禮貌性拜會。馬會同日傍晚6時53分「嚴正澄清」，並無派出任何代表與任何高雄官員會面。高雄新聞局承認「表述不夠完整」，市政府官網同晚7時許刊出的新聞稿，才寫明林雋軒等是「前香港馬會成員」。<br />\n<br />\n（自由時報/香港賽馬會網頁）"},{"pid":"5a063acdb4f783ba7280106ed20c596aea7a065d","tid":1027143,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T15:15:50.000Z","msg":"台版&quot;國師&quot;<br />\n唔記得食藥或飲醉後直播9up"},{"pid":"0cb973b451b8d13677184c6950dafeffefb273e4","tid":1027143,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a063acdb4f783ba7280106ed20c596aea7a065d","tid":1027143,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T15:15:50.000Z","msg":"台版&quot;國師&quot;<br />\n唔記得食藥或飲醉後直播9up"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T15:17:23.000Z","msg":"台灣陳云根黎<br />\n無限鳩UP精神病<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d2cfb16104f917dea161635906e4f1aff2295cb","tid":1027143,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T17:04:52.000Z","msg":"柒撚到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fb925bdb9e4fa2ccdb2f340a2366e3220d9e05c","tid":1027143,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T23:25:10.000Z","msg":"發大財有沒有"},{"pid":"e37c480ac3f4ff9fbaa6f8b25d833cd9bbada96c","tid":1027143,"uid":11285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T23:31:47.000Z","msg":"柒極都選到市長"},{"pid":"87e8b190630e9cda41fe8ef04d6e56eb9e6de971","tid":1027143,"uid":166474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T23:33:37.000Z","msg":"幫高雄搞馬場,賽馬博彩，然後收佢一大筆管理費有冇得諗？係咪怕得罪大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe043eb753e306a61e9e26227e3b961bfc84a131","tid":1027143,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T23:34:27.000Z","msg":"高雄國師想主動將高雄納入大灣區"},{"pid":"ba16d4c5c9017705665746302b0d764bf6dc80f9","tid":1027143,"uid":45232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87e8b190630e9cda41fe8ef04d6e56eb9e6de971","tid":1027143,"uid":166474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T23:33:37.000Z","msg":"幫高雄搞馬場,賽馬博彩，然後收佢一大筆管理費有冇得諗？係咪怕得罪大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T00:02:39.000Z","msg":"兩邊都唔會肯喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}